{"type":"result","subtype":"success","is_error":false,"duration_ms":131129,"duration_api_ms":115555,"num_turns":21,"result":"**Fixed.** The single failing test (`test_plan_interview_stage.sh`) had two issues:\n\n1. **Missing dependency**: Milestone 6 added `write_plan_state()` to `run_plan_interview()`, but the test subprocess didn't source `lib/plan_state.sh` or export `PLAN_STATE_FILE` — so the call failed under `set -euo pipefail`, killing the subprocess before \"Session End\" was logged.\n\n2. **Exit code capture**: Sourcing `plan_interview.sh` applies `set -euo pipefail` to the subprocess. When `run_plan_interview` returned 1 (no DESIGN.md), `set -e` killed the shell before `echo $?` could run. Added `set +e` to safely capture the exit code.\n\nResult: **34/34 tests pass**, shellcheck clean.","stop_reason":"end_turn","session_id":"d1dad49e-983a-472a-a63b-5bfe3e55f42b","total_cost_usd":0.5984750000000001,"usage":{"input_tokens":18,"cache_creation_input_tokens":32560,"cache_read_input_tokens":518020,"output_tokens":5435,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":32560,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"},"modelUsage":{"claude-opus-4-6":{"inputTokens":18,"outputTokens":5435,"cacheReadInputTokens":518020,"cacheCreationInputTokens":32560,"webSearchRequests":0,"costUSD":0.5984750000000001,"contextWindow":200000,"maxOutputTokens":32000}},"permission_denials":[],"fast_mode_state":"off","uuid":"9bd1ebc4-4a9a-4853-a59e-bafb8760355b"}
